name: ANOTHER SPACE
description:
ANOTHER SPACE

I sometimes wear unsophisticated costumes but sometimes I wear dresses with the best weaving in the world.
Which is being limited by social norms and demands.

My own authentic self is actually when I'm all alone
With my freedom of thought.
Exploring the meaning of my own life without many layers that I have to go through.

Liberating the mind until I feel reluctant to hurt others
Liberating the mind until I create happiness that come from myself.



Another Space is a visualization of human ability  to liberate their own thoughts

Digital Illustration 2500 X 2500 px
Translator: Aini Wilinsen
